race.comment: CUMBRIA GEORGE (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (25.29) in a NG at Goulburn. Has a strong record here at this journey including two wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Can discover winning form. ASHBY DOHA (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 2.25 lengths sixth (20.97) but scored four back at this track (20.74). Has a good record here at this journey. Shapes as one to consider. YUNA HERRERA (4) has a strong record this journey here with three wins and a minor from six starts. Recorded a 0.8 lengths win (20.90) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. WHITE AND BLACK (7) has top-three aspirations after placing last time.
